ing: 1 (4.6 ounce) package non-instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "This may not be the best peanut butter pie, but by golly, it's the EZest!!! Cook and serve pudding is combined with peanut butter in this classic made easy."
ins: Prepare cook and serve pudding as directed on package. Stir in peanut butter. Bring mixture to a boil and pour into graham cracker crust. Allow to cool.
